ACT IV. SCENE 3.—VERSES 904-932.

(1) SYNOPSIS. —In this scene Tranio and Theopropides return from their inspection of Simo's house, and discuss it as a bargain. At the end of the scene, Tranio is sent to the farm (l) to fetch his young master back.
